              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2551271-bookchampions?shelf=young-adult">young-adult</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2596346588" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer934472589560688550">I always love reading Woodson&apos;s prose. There is something so effortless and easy and lovely about it—even when the story doesn&apos;t feel complete.<br/><br/><i>From the Notebooks of Melanin Sun</i> is exactly such a book. The ending was a little rushed, and I would have liked a few more &quot;entries&quot; from Mel&apos;s notebook. But it&apos;s hard to fault Woodson, though, for her handling of her subject matter. As an early entry in the growing shelf of LGBTQ+ literature, this one deserves a wider readership.</span>
  <span id="freeText934472589560688550" style="display:none">I always love reading Woodson's prose. There is something so effortless and easy and lovely about it—even when the story doesn't feel complete.<br /><br /><i>From the Notebooks of Melanin Sun</i> is exactly such a book. The ending was a little rushed, and I would have liked a few more "entries" from Mel's notebook. But it's hard to fault Woodson, though, for her handling of her subject matter. As an early entry in the growing shelf of LGBTQ+ literature, this one deserves a wider readership.</span>
  <a data-text-id="934472589560688550" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
